{
	"info": {
		"name": "QuestEval API",
		"description": "Colección completa para probar todos los endpoints del backend de QuestEval.\n\n**Base URL:** `{{baseUrl}}`\n\n**Autenticación:** JWT Bearer Token (obtenido del endpoint de login)\n\n## Módulos:\n1. **Users** - Registro, login, OTP, aprobación de maestros\n2. **Groups** - CRUD de grupos, unirse a grupo, miembros y proyectos del grupo\n3. **Projects** - CRUD de proyectos\n4. **Criteria** - CRUD de criterios de evaluación\n5. **Evaluations** - CRUD de evaluaciones\n6. **Feedback** - CRUD de retroalimentación\n7. **Memberships** - CRUD de membresías\n8. **Storage** - Subida de imágenes",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"auth": {
		"type": "bearer",
		"bearer": [
			{
				"key": "token",
				"value": "{{authToken}}",
				"type": "string"
			}
		]
	},
	"variable": [
		{
			"key": "baseUrl",
			"value": "http://localhost:5122"
		}
	],
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "Users",
			"description": "Endpoints para gestión de usuarios: registro, login, verificación OTP y aprobación de maestros.",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Register",
					"request": {
						"auth": {
							"type": "noauth"
						},
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"estudiante@ejemplo.com\",\n  \"password\": \"ContraseñaSegura123!\",\n  \"fullName\": \"Juan Pérez\",\n  \"role\": \"Alumno\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/Users/register",
							"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
							"path": ["api", "Users", "register"]
						},
						"description": "Registra un nuevo usuario. Roles válidos: `Alumno`, `Profesor`, `Admin`.\n\n- Si el rol es `Profesor`, el `verificationStatus` será `pending` hasta que un Admin lo apruebe.\n- Retorna 400 si el email ya existe."
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "Login",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"type": "text/javascript",
								"exec": [
									"if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
									"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"authToken\", jsonData.token);",
									"    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"userId\", jsonData.userId);",
									"}"
								]
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"auth": {
							"type": "noauth"
						},
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"won.dorado.mid@gmail.com\",\n  \"password\": \"admin123\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/Users/login",
							"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
							"path": ["api", "Users", "login"]
						},
						"description": "Inicia sesión y obtiene un JWT token válido por 7 días.\n\nEl token se guarda automáticamente en la variable `authToken` para usarse en los demás endpoints protegidos."
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "Get All Users",
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/Users",
							"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
							"path": ["api", "Users"]
						},
						"description": "Obtiene la lista de todos los usuarios registrados."
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "Get User by ID",
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/Users/{{userId}}",
							"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
							"path": ["api", "Users", "{{userId}}"]
						},
						"description": "Obtiene un usuario específico por su ID (ObjectId de MongoDB)."
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "Delete User",
					"request": {
						"method": "DELETE",
						"header": [],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/Users/:id",
							"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
							"path": ["api", "Users", ":id"],
							"variable": [
								{
									"key": "id",
									"value": "",
									"description": "ID del usuario a eliminar"
								}
							]
						},
						"description": "Elimina un usuario por ID. Retorna 204 No Content si fue exitoso, 404 si no existe."
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "Send OTP",
					"request": {
						"auth": {
							"type": "noauth"
						},
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"estudiante@ejemplo.com\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/Users/send-otp",
							"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
							"path": ["api", "Users", "send-otp"]
						},
						"description": "Envía un código OTP de 6 dígitos al email proporcionado para verificación."
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "Verify OTP",
					"request": {
						"auth": {
							"type": "noauth"
						},
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"estudiante@ejemplo.com\",\n  \"otpCode\": \"123456\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/Users/verify-otp",
							"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
							"path": ["api", "Users", "verify-otp"]
						},
						"description": "Verifica el código OTP enviado al email. Si es válido, marca el email como verificado."
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "Get Pending Teachers",
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/Users/pending-teachers",
							"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
							"path": ["api", "Users", "pending-teachers"]
						},
						"description": "Obtiene la lista de maestros pendientes de aprobación.\n\n**Requiere:** Rol `Admin` (JWT con claim de rol Admin)."
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "Approve/Reject Teacher",
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"teacherId\": \"<teacher_object_id>\",\n  \"status\": \"approved\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/Users/approve-teacher",
							"host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
							"path": ["api", "Users", "approve-teacher"]
						},
						"description": "Aprueba o rechaza un maestro pendiente.\n\n**Requiere:** Rol `Admin`.\n\nValores válidos para `status`: `approved`, `rejected`."
					},
					"response": []
				}
			]
		},
